  "id": "RAW_ef7ba6ef",
  "title": "上市在即的宇树，走到了哪一步？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mjc1NjM3MjY2MA==&mid=2691566076&idx=1&sn=ad7030233b3c2024af5256d900e1a1b8",
  "date": "2026-03-20 11:36:00",
  "author": "腾讯科技",
  "siteName": "腾讯科技",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"544082422\" data-ratio=\"0.5583333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cfa9bfcc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FQmK3dYQtkw2PRRDb6WJ1t5XydDsRpHyMDVGugLanicOmrzYDalGsATHGItSBUUMxTpMNc6BTtQ4Uz7ib8uGANPp7bPx6YNOa6tUV3t9OndLWI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin: 0pt 8px 24px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-weight: normal;font-style: normal;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);letter-spacing: 0pt;vertical-align: baseline;\" data-font-family=\"default\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">站在交易所门前的王兴兴和宇树机器人。图片由AI生成</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:right;padding-left:8px;padding-right:8px;margin:0 0 8px 0;line-height:1.75;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">文丨苏扬</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:right;padding-left:8px;padding-right:8px;margin:0 0 24px 0;line-height:1.75;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">编辑丨徐青阳</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">宇树终于要兑现上市的承诺了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">3月20日，上交所正式受理宇树科技股份有限公司科创板IPO申请，拟融资金额42.02亿元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“上市没有悬念，有悬念的是会涨多少。”一位与宇树科技合作多年的代理商说。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">根据宇树科技在问询函中披露的数据，其42.02亿元融资将用于投资智能机器人模型研发、本体研发、新产品开发、制造基地建设。公司实现营业收入约17.08 亿元，同比增长335.36%；同期实现扣非后净利润约6亿元，同比增长674.29%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此前一月份，市场一度传出了宇</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:18px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;max-width:100%;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">树上市绿色通道被叫停的消息，彼时宇树科技创始人、CEO王兴兴在朋友圈回应称，“好几周之前的，被人乱编的消息，又扩大了，大家别当真。也不用和外人解释。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">市场传言宇树上市绿色通道被叫停，与对</span></span><span dt-eid=\"em_huaci\" dt-params=\"huaci_type=ai&amp;huaci_name=科创板预先审阅机制\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">科创板预先审阅机制误读有关。该机制面向开展关键核心技术攻关、过早披露信息可能影响经营的科技型企业，在正式申报前参照IPO审核程序，通过问询-回复完成前置把关。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也就是说，这套机制非绿色通道，而是科创板服务硬科技的规范化前置审核环节。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">值得一提的是，近期国产GPU龙头摩尔线程亦采用该机制推进IPO。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">今年以来，大量人形机器人为代表的</span></span><span dt-eid=\"em_huaci\" dt-params=\"huaci_type=ai&amp;huaci_name=具身智能\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">具身智能团队斩获融资，包括亮相春晚的银河通用等都领到了来自投资人的数亿美元“红包”，且多数企业都传言在推动IPO进程，其中宇树把上市说的最为明确。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2025年的世界人形机器人大会上，王兴兴曾表示，“上市是对公司过去九年多发展时间的交代，也是对股东负责的表现。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此次宇树冲刺科创板IPO获得受理，也可以堪称是春晚亮相的之后的一个关键进展。如果闯关成功，宇树科技将成为“</span></span><span dt-eid=\"em_huaci\" dt-params=\"huaci_type=ai&amp;huaci_name=人形机器人第一股\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">人形机器人第一股”。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">宇树在问询函中披露，2025年公司人形机器人出货量超5500台，位居行业第一；2025年1-9月，人形机器人收入占比达51.80%，超越四足机器人成为第一大收入来源，行业级应用收入占比9.01%，其中企业导览场景占行业应用比重50%-70%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就在IPO申请获得受理前不久，王兴兴还受邀以线上的形式参与了</span></span><span dt-eid=\"em_huaci\" dt-params=\"huaci_type=ai&amp;huaci_name=英伟达GTC\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">英伟达GTC大会并发表20多分钟主题为《如何迈过具身智能的</span></span></span><span dt-eid=\"em_huaci\" dt-params=\"huaci_type=ai&amp;huaci_name=ChatGPT时刻\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">ChatGPT时刻》的演讲。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:18px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;max-width:100%;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">王兴兴指出，尽管市场热度不断攀升，但真正具备强泛化能力、能够在陌生环境中稳定执行任务的通用具身智能模型仍未出现，行业整体仍停留在“临界点之前”，未来1至3年将成为决定能否实现突</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">破的关键窗口期。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">王兴兴认为，如果机器人能够在80%的陌生场景中，仅通过语言指令完成80%的任务，即可视为具身智能迈入“确定性时刻”，这一节点将类似大模型领域的ChatGPT时刻，推动行业从展示走向规模化应用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在到达这一确定性时刻之前，跳舞、文旅等场景将是人形机器人的关键应用场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“今年2月，我们的机器人登上央视春晚节目，获得了国内外广泛好评。为了这个节目，我们把能找到的中国传统功夫动作基本都梳理了一遍。”王兴兴在GTC的演讲中表示。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">根据前述代理商提供的数据，春节期间人形机器人租赁的费用在4000-8000元/天不等，“没有绝对标准化，根据客户需求、难度（有所差别）。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于人形机器人应用和商业化，该代理商认为纯市场驱动才可持续，“市场是唯一的炼金石，消费者愿意付费的，不是资本扶持，也不是政府买单。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">值得注意的是，人形机器人在跳舞的过程中，也在不断地推进技术升级迭代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">据王兴兴介绍，为了适应春晚舞台的表演，宇树科技对机器人也做了专门改装，其中包括激光雷达的升级改造、预训练的全身模型等等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:18px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:QQNewsCustomFont, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, roboto, helvetica, arial, avenir, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, stheiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 24px;letter-spacing:0.5px;line-height:1.75em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“我们还开发了全身状态感知模型，让机器人更好地完成感知与决策；同时搭建了集群控制系统，可以调度几十台、上百台机器人完成复杂走位与编队表演。”王兴兴说。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
